<main class="main-content">
	<h1>Hi, I'm Rohin</h1>
	<p>
		I'm a builder and thinker interested in software, design, and the
		intersection of technology with everyday life. I spend most of my time
		writing code, reading widely, and exploring ideas that sit at the edges
		of disciplines.
	</p>
	<p>
		This site is a home for my writing and projects — a place to think out
		loud about the things I'm learning and making. I believe in working in
		public, learning by doing, and the quiet power of showing up
		consistently.
	</p>
	<p>
		When I'm not at a keyboard, you'll find me going on walks, cooking
		something new, or buried in a good book. Feel free to look around.
	</p>
</main>

<style>
	.main-content {
		max-width: 640px;
		margin: 0 auto;
		padding: 4rem 2rem;
	}

	h1 {
		font-family: var(--font-heading);
		font-size: 2rem;
		font-weight: 600;
		margin: 0 0 1.5rem 0;
		color: var(--text);
	}

	p {
		margin: 0 0 1.25rem 0;
		color: var(--text);
		font-size: 1.05rem;
		line-height: 1.7;
	}

	@media (max-width: 768px) {
		.main-content {
			padding: 2rem 1.5rem;
		}

		h1 {
			font-size: 1.6rem;
		}
	}
</style>
